	(103, 2, '<b>Rigatoni Pasta Sauce Nugget "S"</b>', 'rigatoni-pasta-sauce-nugget-s.html', '<b>Rigatoni Pasta Sauce Nugget "S"</b>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '<p><span style="font-size: 14pt; background-color: #f1c40f;" data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt; background-color: #f1c40f;"><strong><span style="color: #000000;" data-mce-style="color: #000000;">&nbsp;Ingredients : </span>&nbsp;</strong></span></p><ul><li><span>470 gr </span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" data-mce-style="color: #000000;"><strong><a href="http://manifesto.co.id/clients/belfoods//products/royal/belfoods-royal-chicken-nugget-s/#sthash.onCy7OHb.dpbs" data-mce-href="http://manifesto.co.id/clients/belfoods//products/royal/belfoods-royal-chicken-nugget-s/#sthash.onCy7OHb.dpbs" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" data-mce-style="color: #000000;">ROYAL CHICKEN NUGGET "S"</a></strong></span></li><li><span>1 sendok makan margarin</span></li><li><span>1 buah bawang bombay,cincang halus</span></li><li><span>2 siung bawang putih,memarkan</span></li><li><span>1 sendok teh italian seasoning</span></li><li><span>4 sendok makan saus sambal</span></li><li><span>2 sendok makan saus tomat</span></li><li><span>ÃÂ½ buah paprika merah, iris tipis</span></li><li><span>ÃÂ½ buah paprika hijau, iris tipis</span></li><li><span>Garam, gula pasir, dan merica bubuk secukupnya</span></li><li><span>200 gr pasta rigatoni, rebuslalu tiriskan</span></li></ul><p><span style="font-size: 14pt; background-color: #f1c40f;" data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt; background-color: #f1c40f;"><strong><span style="color: #000000;" data-mce-style="color: #000000;">&nbsp;How to Make :</span>&nbsp;</strong></span></p><ol><li><span>Panaskan margarin, lalu tumis bawang bombay, bawang putih, dan italian seasoning hingga harum.&nbsp;Masukkan saus sambal dan saus tomat, aduk rata.</span></li><li><span>Tambahkan merica, garam, gula pasir, dan paprika, aduk hingga matang.&nbsp;Angkat.</span></li><li><span>Susun pasta yang sudah direbus di atas piring saji,lalu tuang dengan saus dan taburi dengan <strong>ROYAL CHICKEN NUGGET "S"</strong>.</span></li><li><span>Sajikan dengan taburan keju parut.</span></li></ol>', '', '2019-01-01 00:00:00', 'https://belfoods.com/id/public/content/Foto-Resep-NuggetS-Pasta.jpg', '', '', 1, 7, 1, 'admin', '2026-03-16 16:27:58', '2026-03-16 16:27:58'),
	(104, 2, '<b>Nasi Kuning Gulung Isi Nugget Stick</b>', 'nasi-kuning-gulung-isi-nugget-stick.html', '<b>Nasi Kuning Gulung Isi Nugget Stick</b>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '<p><span style="font-size: 14pt; background-color: #f1c40f;" data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt; background-color: #f1c40f;"><strong><span style="color: #000000;" data-mce-style="color: #000000;">&nbsp;Ingredients : </span>&nbsp;</strong></span></p><ul><li><span>470 gr </span><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" data-mce-style="color: #000000;"><a href="http://manifesto.co.id/clients/belfoods//products/uenaaak/chicken-stick-3/#sthash.Lc92YJyS.dpbs" data-mce-href="http://manifesto.co.id/clients/belfoods//products/uenaaak/chicken-stick-3/#sthash.Lc92YJyS.dpbs" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" data-mce-style="color: #000000;">ROYAL CHICKEN NUGGET STICK</a></span></strong></li><li><span>100 gr beras ketan, rendam</span></li><li><span>100 gr beras</span></li><li><span>250 ml santan cair</span></li><li><span>3 cm kunyit, haluskan</span></li><li><span>3 lembar daun jeruk</span></li><li><span>Garam secukupnya</span></li><li><span>5 lembar telur dadar tipis</span></li></ul><p><span style="font-size: 14pt; background-color: #f1c40f;" data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt; background-color: #f1c40f;"><strong><span style="color: #000000;" data-mce-style="color: #000000;">&nbsp;How to Make :</span>&nbsp;</strong></span></p><ol><li><span>Campur beras ketan, beras,santan cair, kunyit, daun jeruk, dan garam, masak hingga menjadi aron lalu kukus hingga matang.</span></li><li><span>Ambil selembar dadar telur lalu beri nasi kuning, ratakan. Masukkan <strong><span style="color: #000000;" data-mce-style="color: #000000;"><a href="http://manifesto.co.id/clients/belfoods//products/uenaaak/chicken-stick-3/#sthash.Lc92YJyS.dpbs" style="color: #000000;" data-mce-href="http://manifesto.co.id/clients/belfoods//products/uenaaak/chicken-stick-3/#sthash.Lc92YJyS.dpbs" data-mce-style="color: #000000;">ROYAL CHICKEN NUGGET STICK</a></span></strong> goreng di tengahnya.</span></li><li><span>Gulung hingga padat dan rapi, potong-potong dan sajikan.</span></li></ol>', '', '2019-01-01 00:00:00', 'https://belfoods.com/id/public/content/Foto-Resep-NasiKuning.jpg', '', '', 1, 6, 1, 'admin', '2026-03-16 16:28:01', '2026-03-16 16:28:01'),
	(105, 2, '<b>Cordon Bleu With Tomato Sauce</b>', 'cordon-bleu-with-tomato-sauce.html', '<b>Cordon Bleu With Tomato Sauce</b>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '<p><span style="font-size: 14pt; background-color: #f1c40f;" data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt; background-color: #f1c40f;"><strong><span style="color: #000000;" data-mce-style="color: #000000;">&nbsp;Ingredients : </span>&nbsp;</strong></span></p><ul><li><span>250 gr </span><span style="color: #000000;" data-mce-style="color: #000000;"><strong><a href="http://manifesto.co.id/clients/belfoods//products/royal/belfoods-royal-chicken-nugget-s/#sthash.onCy7OHb.dpbs" style="color: #000000;" data-mce-href="http://manifesto.co.id/clients/belfoods//products/royal/belfoods-royal-chicken-nugget-s/#sthash.onCy7OHb.dpbs" data-mce-style="color: #000000;">ROYAL CORDON BLEU</a></strong></span></li><li><span>Minyak goreng secukupnya</span></li><li><span>200 gr spageti, rebus matang</span></li><li><span>1 sendok makan peterseli cincang<br><br>Tomato Sauce :<br></span></li><li><span>2 sendok makan margarin</span></li><li><span>ÃÂ½ buah bawang bombay,cincang halus</span></li><li><span>1 siung bawang putih, cincang halus</span></li><li><span>2 buah tomat, potong dadu</span></li><li><span>5 sendok makan saus tomat</span></li><li><span>2 sendok makan saus sambal</span></li><li><span>Garam, gula pasir, dan merica </span><span>bubuk secukupnya</span></li></ul><p><span style="font-size: 14pt; background-color: #f1c40f;" data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt; background-color: #f1c40f;"><strong><span style="color: #000000;" data-mce-style="color: #000000;">&nbsp;How to Make :</span>&nbsp;</strong></span></p><ol><li><span>Panaskan minyak, goreng <span style="color: #000000;" data-mce-style="color: #000000;"><strong><a href="http://manifesto.co.id/clients/belfoods//products/royal/belfoods-royal-chicken-nugget-s/#sthash.onCy7OHb.dpbs" style="color: #000000;" data-mce-href="http://manifesto.co.id/clients/belfoods//products/royal/belfoods-royal-chicken-nugget-s/#sthash.onCy7OHb.dpbs" data-mce-style="color: #000000;">ROYAL CORDON BLEU</a></strong></span> hingga matang. Angkat dan tiriskan.</span></li><li><span>Saus tomat: Panaskan margarin, tumis bawang bombay dan bawang putih hingga harum. Masukkan tomat, saus tomat, saus sambal, garam, gula pasir, dan merica bubuk. Masak hingga matang, angkat.</span></li><li><span> Susun spageti dan <span style="color: #000000;" data-mce-style="color: #000000;"><strong><a href="http://manifesto.co.id/clients/belfoods//products/royal/belfoods-royal-chicken-nugget-s/#sthash.onCy7OHb.dpbs" style="color: #000000;" data-mce-href="http://manifesto.co.id/clients/belfoods//products/royal/belfoods-royal-chicken-nugget-s/#sthash.onCy7OHb.dpbs" data-mce-style="color: #000000;">ROYAL CORDON BLEU</a></strong></span> dalam piring saji, lalu tuang saus tomat di atasnya. Taburi dengan peterseli cincang, sajikan.</span></li></ol>', '', '2019-01-01 00:00:00', 'https://belfoods.com/id/public/content/Foto-Resep-CordonBleu-Tomato1.jpg', '', '', 1, 8, 1, 'admin', '2026-03-16 16:28:01', '2026-03-16 16:28:01'),
